        "comment": {
            "name": "comment",
            "type": "com.atlassian.jira.issue.fields.CommentSystemField",
            "value": [
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/40196",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=zm",
                        "name": "zm",
                        "displayName": "Mz",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Hi,\r\n\r\nI think I found the problem.\r\n\r\nZend\/View\/Abstract.php on line 115:\r\n\r\nprivate $_encoding = 'UTF-8'; \r\n\r\nI changed the value for:\r\nprivate $_encoding = 'ISO-8859-1';\r\n\r\nAnd now it works correctly.\r\nAll accents are back.\r\n\r\nBut I work with the charset ISO-8859-1:\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text\/html; charset=ISO-8859-1\" \/> \r\n\r\nIf I change the charset for UTF-8 I have to modify again the line 115 to the value 'UTF-8'.\r\n\r\nIt seems that the encoding is not modified dynamically in the file Abstract.php when it changed from the layout manually.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=zm",
                        "name": "zm",
                        "displayName": "Mz",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-04-23T11:08:03.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-04-23T11:08:03.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/40198",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "This was called out in the README.txt for 1.9.7, as well as in the public release announcements and an additional security announcement. Due to security issues with inconsistencies in encoding across components, we updated all components to use UTF-8 by default, while making it possible to configure encoding on encoding-aware components. \r\n\r\nFor the view object, you can do this with:\r\n{code}\r\n$view->setEncoding('ISO-8859-1');\r\n{code}\r\nor from your application.ini:\r\n{code}\r\nresources.view.encoding = \"ISO-8859-1\"\r\n{code}",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-04-23T11:53:00.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-04-23T11:53:00.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/40199",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=zm",
                        "name": "zm",
                        "displayName": "Mz",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "OK thanks a lot Matthew.\r\n\r\nIt works perfectly.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=zm",
                        "name": "zm",
